                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2000-05-05</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>This book is far better than any of the general trekking in Nepal books if you are heading to the Everest region. The itineraries are great. The maps are very helpful and the directions completely eliminate the need for a guide. If you are planning on heading to the Everest area, this is a must have.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">The definitive book on trekking in the Everest region</div>
